    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You raise one Medium or Small humanoid corpse as a @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.monsters.Actor.OBujQLLPSmlJiZnL]{ghoul} under your control. Any class levels or abilities the creature had in life are gone, replaced by the standard ghoul stat block.<br><em><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></em> When you cast this spell using a 3rd-level spell slot, it can be used on the corpse of a Large humanoid to create a Large ghoul. When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, this spell creates a @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.monsters.Actor.IyIybE5t2adMEVUM]{ghast}, but the material component changes to an onyx gemstone worth at least 200 gp.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
